Class Loader

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ClassLoader
      • nl.tudelft.dcsc.sr2jlib.instance.Loader

  • public class Loader
extends ClassLoader
    The class loading for individuals NOTE: This class re-uses the internal byte buffer for efficiency, this is why it is solely targeting the individual classes. I.e. we expect the loadClass method NOT to be called recursively!
    Author:
    Dr. Ivan S. Zapreev
